{"tid":2044080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"房協幫港共打壓良心黃店（修正後重開）","createTime":"2020-05-31T00:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T01:31:46.000Z","uid":35814,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"710b40d5a845b594ece7ad7a8637cff0d9c26815","tid":2044080,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:56:34.000Z","msg":"原文同link照搬過來<br />\n所以好多emoji<br />\n請見諒<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1970276573232191/posts/2591612124431963/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1970276573232191%2Fposts%2F2591612124431963%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=01322311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1970276573232191/posts/2591612124431963/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n今日係2020年5月31日，亦係牛頭角，膳心小館倒閉前的183天⏰。<br />\n昨日下午，房協新任經理，趁我唔喺舖的時候，得意洋洋地交咗封信俾我哋餐廳經理。同一時間，打埋電話通知膳心當區的肥仔區議員 Lee Kwan Chak 李軍澤 ，房協決定今年11月30日收番膳心牛頭角舖位，房協話自己營運返喎。<br />\n係，👉房協將正式收番膳心間舖👈<br />\n係，房協經理在我未拆信前，已就將消息告知其他人。<br />\n封信好奇怪🤔，簽署人連名都唔敢出，亦唔敢寫職位，做法十分古怪。<br />\n不過，反正房協要在彩頣居，每年虧蝕數百萬情況下，租都唔要，自己接管番嚟做。原因係乜，有腦的人都會明白。房協收舖決定，直接打爛了我哋五十多位被政府排斥的手足飯碗;亦直接影響區內一群依靠我哋派飯服務的清貧長者。<br />\n究竟邊個用盡千方百計破壞黃色經濟圈及政治打壓，大家心中有數。我哋會在餘下日子，嚴肅、公開及依法處理與房協職員的每項分歧。同時，亦會繼續幫助區內有需要的人士，令佢哋得到溫飽。<br />\n至於，膳心會否離棄九龍灣街坊🤔？我哋會盡力在呢段時間，盡力透過賣蛋卷、小食及樓面餐飲服務，賺多一些錢，嘗試在區內另覓地方，繼續服務。今年，我哋會提早接受預訂月餅，等一眾手足可以賺多個錢。同時，大家的支持亦直接影響膳心的發展。而未來的星期六日及假期，亦會繼續將零食現貨發售。我哋對於一直企在市民一方，我哋無怨無悔。多謝大家一直的支持。<br />\n膳心腦細<br />\n#一間被打壓小店 #膳心小館<br />\n#黃色經濟圈 #政治打壓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehyMz1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FehyMz1O.jpg&h=8593a2a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fdc6c712074aa12a01654741e46770175406120","tid":2044080,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:57:07.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n正話寫錯左房署<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d92e1a3415a53446a52728ac9e43c99eea9e50","tid":2044080,"uid":252142,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T00:58:15.000Z","msg":"房協呢個毒榴一定要剷 我會幫你同林奠反映下"},{"pid":"2e07c41fd1c361a6ed9d7392aa0ec80a88d2dbe1","tid":2044080,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T01:00:21.000Z","msg":"房協都要奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcefc8c426bb6af9125a0c4a651bd96c1b653a2d","tid":2044080,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T01:00:21.000Z","msg":"港共已經開始要搞黃店<br />\n留意下大家身邊黃店有冇類似情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea7d3aee39232e37d9a305ae023f4345401d652","tid":2044080,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"同一時間，北角健康邨班住戶屌緊房協理財無方<br />\n<br />\n呢期房協係咪食撚咗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc58d449e199d07bb4b33a62885004056609777","tid":2044080,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T01:03:42.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec768bd39eefc06b69e34c25044873bf6c3901b","tid":2044080,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T01:04:37.000Z","msg":"天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4619cb50acc90a58f8a66e9ee9bf94061510ae48","tid":2044080,"uid":122205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T01:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdd1c3d224dde8b5f196248069eea760f3950e8","tid":2044080,"uid"